Laxalt to Sky: &quot;Romagnoli at 24 has the personality of an old player. He is a very serious hard worker and this is very important. Seeing the captain working in a certain way and having this personality gives you the idea of what a captain is.&quot;<br />
<br />
Laxalt: &quot;He [Romagnoli] is a point of reference for us, he helps us a lot. It's what's needed for this team, in this sense he helps a lot. He is very young but he has the mentality of the desire to keep growing and this is very positive.&quot;
